---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service - CountTrackula">
  <section class="tos">
    <h1>Terms of Service for CountTrackula</h1>
    <p class="effective-date"><strong>Effective Date: 2025-01-01</strong></p>

    <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>By using CountTrackula, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please discontinue use of the app.</p>

    <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
    <p>CountTrackula is a free progressive web app (PWA) that allows you to track personal metrics such as fitness, nutrition, habits, and health markers. It stores data locally on your device and optionally syncs to your personal Google Drive.</p>

    <h2>3. Use of the App</h2>
    <p>CountTrackula is provided for personal, non-commercial use. You agree not to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Use the app for any unlawful purpose</li>
      <li>Attempt to reverse engineer, decompile, or modify the app</li>
      <li>Use the app in any way that could harm Fish Sauce Games or other users</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Health Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>CountTrackula is a personal tracking tool only. It is not a medical device and does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult a qualified healthcare professional before making decisions based on data tracked in the app.</p>

    <h2>5. Your Data</h2>
    <p>Your tracking data belongs to you. CountTrackula stores data locally on your device. If you use Google Drive sync, your data is stored in your own Google Drive account. Fish Sauce Games does not access, own, or control your data. See our <a href="/CountTrackula/PrivacyPolicy">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.</p>

    <h2>6. Google Drive</h2>
    <p>If you choose to use Google Drive sync, your use of Google Drive is also subject to <a href="https://policies.google.com/terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Terms of Service</a>. Fish Sauce Games is not affiliated with Google.</p>

    <h2>7. Availability</h2>
    <p>We strive to keep CountTrackula available, but we do not guarantee uninterrupted access. We may update, modify, or discontinue the app at any time without notice.</p>

    <h2>8. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
    <p>CountTrackula is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied. Fish Sauce Games does not warrant that the app will be error-free, secure, or suitable for your particular purpose.</p>

    <h2>9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, Fish Sauce Games shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of CountTrackula, including but not limited to loss of data.</p>

    <h2>10. Changes to These Terms</h2>
    <p>We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Continued use of the app after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the new terms.</p>

    <h2>11. Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:</p>
    <p>Fish Sauce Games<br />Justin@FishSauceGames.com</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .tos {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .tos h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tos h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tos p {
    color: #c0c8d8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tos ul {
    color: #c0c8d8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tos ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .tos a {
    color: #e05252;
  }

  .tos a:hover {
    color: #ff7070;
  }

  .effective-date {
    color: #6b7a99 !important;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
